'Therefore prepare your minds for action.<f caller="+"> <fr>1:13 </fr><ft>literally, "gird up the waist of your mind" or "put on the belt of the waist of your mind"</ft></f> Be sober, and set your hope fully on the grace that will be brought to you at the revelation of Yeshua the Messiah—',
